    {
      "title": "Discover Color Theory Through Exploration",
      "text": [
        "The core color selection tool is the basic color wheel, built on fundamental color theory. It includes standard options like complementary, analogous, and triadic schemes. Users click around, experiment with different combinations, and instantly see the results of their choices."
     
